title: 1 Bedroom Apartment - North Beacon Hill
posting_body: ['The Beacon Point Apartments sit in the sweet, neighborly community of North Beacon Hill.', 'Well placed in close proximity to I-5, I-90, and Downtown enjoy a quick commute to all that Seattle has to offer.', 'A fully renovated mid-century building, Beacon Point offers a bright, white, modern aesthetic with classic subway tile; natural light; new appliances; and an upgraded lighting package in a spacious floor plan.', 'Community amenities include building laundry operated by an app on your smartphone; storage lockers, and professional management.', '+1bd/1ba', '+ Laundry on-site (App payments!)', '+Vinyl Plank Flooring & Carpet', '+Parking waitlisted $50 when available', 'Additional Info:', '+ Utilities: $80 for 1 Person, $130 for 2 Persons +$30 per additional', '+Electricity (Seattle City Light) & Internet - Resident responsibility', 'Move In Info:', '+Application fee: $50', '+Holding fee: $500', '+Refundable Security Deposit: 75% of 1 month’s rent', 'We are a pet friendly property!', 'No restrictions!', '+Pet rent is $50 per month+$200 refundable pet deposit']
